# Canonical URL: https://esrf.net/
# All other public host/scheme variants must 301 to it (path + query preserved).
# Cloudflare's "Always Use HTTPS" normally upgrades http://* to https://* at
# the edge before this file is consulted, but we still list every variant
# explicitly as defence in depth in case that toggle is ever disabled or a
# browser hits a cached parking-style A record. :splat preserves the path;
# Cloudflare preserves query strings on 301 responses automatically.
https://www.esrf.net/* https://esrf.net/:splat 301
http://www.esrf.net/*  https://esrf.net/:splat 301
http://esrf.net/*      https://esrf.net/:splat 301

